From: radhevrishi <radhev.232@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 26 May 2026 11:04:54 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] patch 0874: critical client bugs + hydration mismatches

- movers useWindowWidth: SSR mismatch fixed (always 1024 init, then effect)
- orders fetchConcallData: silent no-op fixed (deps now [screenerStocks.length])
- MultibaggerAnalytics: usaRows + prevScoreMap reactive to LS changes via dataTick
- DashboardClient hasToken: SSR-safe init via state + effect
- watchlists convictionEntries: SSR-safe init (lazy-init was reading LS)
- Home greeting + clock: deferred to post-mount (no hydration mismatch)
- GlobalSearch focus timer: cleanup on unmount
